org.apache.hawq.pxf.plugins.hive

Class HiveFilterBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hawq.pxf.plugins.hive.HiveFilterBuilder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FilterParser.FilterBuilder

    public class HiveFilterBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
implements FilterParser.FilterBuilder
    Uses the filter parser code to build a filter object, either simple - a single FilterParser.BasicFilter object or a compound - a List of FilterParser.BasicFilter objects. HiveAccessor will use the filter for partition filtering.
